{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act26side", "eventName": "空想花庭", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HE-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "願跟隨主", "storyInfo": "孩子們帶來了他們暖洋洋的被褥。他們說，給這個叔叔蓋上吧，他睡在這裡會著涼的。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$gardener_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們對生活應該是有所憧憬的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這話說起來好奇怪，這難道不是理所當然的嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果對生活沒有半點期待，那我們又為什麼要擁有生命，降生在這世上呢？總不至於就是為了來受苦的吧？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你看，孩子們就不會考慮這樣奇怪的問題。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "童年是多麼無憂無慮的一段時光啊，只有脫離童年的人，才能明白那時候的好。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這話放在少年、青年時，也都適用。當時總覺得有許多煩惱，可等之後回頭再看看，那時候的小煩惱，算得了什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那個時候，我們都有使不完的力氣，總想去做點什麼，總相信生活能越來越好。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們是如此認真，如此努力地在生活。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "真奇怪，所有事情難道不是都應該越來越好嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "很難說是從什麼時候開始，我像是已經喪失了憧憬未來的力氣。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "能容納我的空間越來越窄小，能供我呼吸的空氣越來越稀薄。我的生活變得沉重，變得能夠看到盡頭，變得......不再有希望。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "就像從山上向下滾落的石頭。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "誰都知道石頭不會停止，只會不斷下落。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "直到摔個粉碎。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g3_abandonsancturay_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的花......都沒了啊。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別再往前走了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此處建築結構遭到多次破壞，具有高度不穩定性......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.5, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——！", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒，回來。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，費德里科先生......我想......再找找看。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說過的，這裡沒有你想要的花了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我就是想確認......所有的花都死了。沒有一朵......任何一朵......幸運地得救。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbreak", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......哈......哈......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法解析你的行為。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我親手種出的花......代表友誼和希望。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可人們早就不再在意這些，沒有人再關注花期，他們遺忘了最不該忘記的事。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道不可笑嗎？竟然有人懷疑萊蒙德會放火，就因為他是薩卡茲？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們明明在一起生活了這麼久。越是困難的時刻，我們越該相互依偎......這是主教閣下說的話。我很想相信......我本該相信。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而事實就擺在我面前，我無法扭過頭去。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為何隔閡始終存在？人與人是不是註定無法彼此理解？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一點點的混亂，就足以讓表面上的秩序走向崩塌，而一旦陷入混亂，人們就會互相傷害......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了......我已經忍耐夠久了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#6$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒跌跌撞撞地來到了被大火燒毀的聖像面前。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡沒有第二朵幸運的花，只有一個破舊的木盤，裡面盛著幾片乾癟的麵包。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他將那氣味有些古怪的麵包放入口中咀嚼。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是略有些腥鹹，帶著海潮一樣苦澀的滋味。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳，難吃......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒，把你手中的東西放下。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放下？這可不行......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨夜，我本想去告解，結果無意中聽到主教閣下的計劃......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來想，至少杰拉爾德他們不用參與進來，他們本來就要走了不是嗎？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但為什麼......最後會變成這樣？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會吃完這些東西。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你並不是為了延續自己的生命。為何還要嘗試轉化？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想求一個答案。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想知道，這世上到底有沒有能救我們的存在。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科知道，自己現在必須要阻止眼前的這個人。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現實是，他站在原地沒有動。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾步之外，阿爾圖羅奏響了她的樂器，琴聲劃破寂靜的帷幕，其中的情感費德里科不明白，也從不試圖明白。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是頭一次，執行者無法掌控自己的行動。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他開始無法理解自己。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為什麼他沒有在見到對方的第一時間就動手？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為什麼這個瘦弱的男人吃下了可以把人變成怪物的東西，現在卻什麼都沒有發生？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樂曲被拉高了一個音調。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "音符間彌散的沉默像是某種笑話。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......這是，血？", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這算什麼，只是這樣而已嗎？只是，咳咳，只是這樣，算什麼......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼吸頻率加快，剛剛的撞擊有造成下呼吸道或肺部出血的可能性，不採取措施的話可能引發窒息。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你需要立刻接受治療。在此之前，我會先對你進行急救。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，咳咳、我......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i11", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 35.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒抬手捂住嘴，儘量壓低咳嗽的聲音。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但血仍然很快溢出手掌，帶著令人不舒服的黏膩，順著指縫往下淌。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他踉蹌著後退一步，摔倒在破損的聖像前。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被他燒毀的聖像這時彷彿又接納了他這個失去了力氣的兇手，聖像的斷臂落在兩側，好似一個輕柔的抱擁。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒感到一陣奇異的溫暖。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......哈哈......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是什麼事都沒有嗎......？", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果連這個也是假的，主教閣下他受到了欺騙，根本沒有什麼神明......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你吃下的東西是出自海洋的某種殘渣，有極大機率引起生理層面上的變異，但從來都與你口中的神明無關。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......多可笑啊......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的狀態很糟糕。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依照目前的速度惡化下去，你將會進入休克狀態，死亡的風險很大。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？那真......不錯......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果你想要留下任何遺囑，我可以作為你的遺囑執行人為你服務。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺囑......？", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有什麼要留下的......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭人......我們的樂園是虛假的，你們的信仰是虛假的。", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "友誼、信賴、期盼、未來......什麼都沒有了，沒人能真的得救......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人......沒有人能真正獲得救贖......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一種選擇嗎？這是某種好的結局嗎？"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者站在原地，沒有再上前。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論如何，所有的苦痛都逐漸遠去。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疲憊的花匠終於合上眼。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g1_monasteryentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#2$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "餘音還在迴盪，我還能感受到......最後一刻琴弦傳導至指尖的震顫，尖銳得幾乎能割破皮膚的尾音。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是最初，那旋律平靜如涓流。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個原本平凡的人，用自己的生命證明了一件事——並不存在什麼拯救者。他頑強的精神戰勝了變化中的肉體。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多麼美妙的音樂......這就是人類堅韌又自由的精神，與那些可悲的海洋生物截然不同。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這首曲子將把他的故事帶給所有人。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們將理解他的情感，稱頌他的意志，讚美他的勇氣。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒·杜波瓦將被世人銘記。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你說是不是，費德里科？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_sys_act26side_intro", "key": "$m_sys_act26side_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i12", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 0.85, "yScaleTo": 0.85, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為你會在那裡多留一會，畢竟你好像十分在意那位死者......甚至認為他的事務優先順序高於對我的追捕。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科，你學會哀憐了嗎？還是說，你依然和過去一樣，識別不出他人的喜怒哀樂，與眾人格格不入？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通緝犯阿爾圖羅，你的源石技藝又一次引導了他人的死亡。我不可能放過射程範圍內最大的威脅。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依據拉特蘭律法，你的刑期會再次增加。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "求死是他的個人意志，即使沒有我的演奏，他也會走上這條路。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次又一次，我只不過揭示了這些可憐人內心的瘡疤，旁人卻要扭過頭去。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也和其他人一樣，被他的經歷刺痛了嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科，你是不是至今仍然不理解無法按捺的衝動？像那位主教堅持走上一條荊棘之路......", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......像我不能自已地想要演奏他們的情緒。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的確不能理解。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理解與否，並不影響律法的執行。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我是為了克萊芒得到應有的處置而前往聖堂。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他罪不至死。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——哦？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想拯救一個意圖自毀的人。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你沒有發現嗎？這個念頭並不合乎邏輯。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒說，在看似完美的事物上，傷痕一旦出現就無法挽回。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我會驗證這句話的正確性。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科，你好像確實變得有趣了那麼一點點......只是一點點而已。或許等下次見面的時候，我就能彈奏出你的思緒......", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，我該結束這趟旅程了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g1_monasteryentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問，是阿爾圖羅小姐嗎？", "name": "“大貴族使者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恭候多時。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很抱歉，明明是我們主動邀請您做客，我卻來得有些遲了，這裡非常難找。", "name": "“大貴族使者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唔，我是不是來得不是時候？", "name": "“大貴族使者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科！", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這真是，看一眼就會讓人頭痛三天的畫面。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科，你怎麼和阿爾圖羅對上了？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早上好，拉特蘭的先生們。", "name": "“大貴族使者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早上好，這位......女士。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（費德里科，她身上的紋章屬於某位選帝侯！）", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在不能直接對阿爾圖羅動手，這可能會影響拉特蘭和萊塔尼亞之間的關係......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我拒絕你的提議。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們商量好了嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不如，費德里科，我給你一次機會，如何？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果想要對我舉起銃，你該瞄準的是這裡......", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "n", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "n", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$shotgunreload", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑髮女人捧起執行者握緊銃的手。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她讓銃口抵住自己的前額。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要扣下扳機，銃的彈丸就會貫穿我的頭顱，從此之後，我就不會再是你的困擾......費德里科，你想要這麼做嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不要試試看？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要將通緝犯逮捕，非必要情況，一般不建議直接擊斃。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你的說辭很合理。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunsingle", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_magic_shield_02", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_5", "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真動手？！都和你說了會是國際問題了！", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，奧倫，好像事情沒那麼嚴重......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，她不會有事。你不瞭解這個女人。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，只是玩一個小遊戲罷了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅小姐，這是某種源石技藝的應用效果嗎？", "name": "“大貴族使者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便如此，剛剛的舉動也太過危險了。", "name": "“大貴族使者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您的關心，如果還有下一次，我會注意的。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科，就當作我給你留下的線索吧。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有想過，演奏從未停止，只是你聽不見？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是不到最精彩最宏大的段落時，所有人都聽不見？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，樂聲已盡，我也該再次出發了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#8$1"}, {